               <msContents>
                  <summary>The Revelaton of John. Acts of Lalibela. Story of Mary. Vision of John, Son of Thunder. On the Dual Virginity of Mary. Chants called Mäwaś‘ǝt chants.  Excerpt of Prayer to Fanuel. Book of healing. Commentary on Prayer of the Covenant. Discussion of the Seven Signs from the Book of Revelation. Prescription for Protection in Travel. Collection of Notes on Various Topics.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="43r" facs="003"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT3179Revela"/>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">ዘዮሐንስ: መጥሮጶሊስ: ዘቁስጥንጥ(ን)ያ: ኤጲስቆጶስ: አመ: ሀለዎ: ይሰደድ: ራእዩ: ለዮሐንስ: አቡቀለምሲስ: ዘከመ: ርእዮ: ለኢየሱስ: ክርስቶስ: ከመ: ያጠይቆሙ: ለአግብርቲሁ: ዘይመጽእ: ወሀለዎ: ይኩን: ፍጡነ: ወእምድኅሬሁ: ኃተሞሙ:<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="44r" to="54v" facs="046"/><title>Acts of Lalibela, Gädlä Lalibela, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ገድለ፡ ላሊበላ፡</foreign></title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="55r" to="60v" facs="057"/><title>Story of Mary, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ነገረ፡ ማርያም።</foreign></title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">ወበሳድስ: ወርኅ: ተፈነወ: ገብርኤል መ: እምኀበ: እግዚአብሔር: ዘይቤ: እምጽንሰ: ኤልሳቤጥ: መካን: ው: ዘዜነወ: ለዘካ: በውስተ: ቅዱሳን: ወእምዝ: መጽአ: ገብርኤል: ኅበ: ማርያም: ድ: አምሳለ: አረጋዊ: ልሂቅ: ብሂለ: ገብርኤልኒ: ሰብእ: ወአምላክ: ውእቱ:</incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4"><locus from="61r" to="64r" facs="063"/><title>Vision of John, Son of Thunder, on the Dual Virginity of Mary, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ራእይ: ዘዮሐንስ:</foreign></title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ: አብ: ወወልድ:<gap reason="omitted"/> ራእይ: ዘዮሐንስ: ወልደ: ነጎድጓድ: ዘርእየ: ተአምሪሃ: ለእግዝእትነ: ማርያም: ይቤ: ርእኩ: አስትአየ: ተአምር: ዐቢይ: በውስተ: ሰማይ: ብእሲተ: እንተ: ትለብስ: ፀሐየ: ወወርኃ: ታሕተ: እገሪሃ:<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5"><locus from="65r" to="98r" facs="067"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT1990Mawase">, with musical notation</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i6"><locus from="98v" facs="101"/><title type="incomplete" ref="LIT2765RepCh49"/>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Excerpt from Greeting to Fanu’el</note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i7"><locus from="99r" to="106v" facs="101"/><title>Ritual for the Unction of the Sick, Mäṣḥafä Baḥrǝy, <foreign xml:lang="gez">መጽሐፈ: ባሕርይ</foreign></title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ: አብ:ወወልድ:<gap reason="omitted"/> ዝንቱ: መጽሐፈ: ባሕርይ:: ዘተሠርዓ: እምአበዊነ: ቅዱሳን: ሐዋርያት: ዘተውህበ: ለነ: ለክርስቲያን: ለተፈውሶ: እምደዌ: ሥጋ: ወነፍስ: ወለሥርየተ: ኃጢ: ምስለ: ተአምኖ: ኃጣውእ: ለካህናት:<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i8"><locus from="107r" to="107v" facs="109"/><title>Excerpt from the Commentary on Prayer of the Covenant, Tǝrgwami Ṣälotä Kidan, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ትርጓሜ፡ ጸሎተ፡ ኪዳን፡</foreign>. Commentary on the Missal, in Gǝ‘ǝz (the missal) and Amharic (the commentary)</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i9"><locus from="107v" to="108v" facs="110"/><title>Excerpt from the Gǝ‘ǝz commentary on the Book of Revelation</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i10"><locus from="108v" facs="110"/><title type="incomplete" ref="LIT1171Awdana"/>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Excerpt from Cycle of Kings</note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i11"><locus from="110r" to="110v" facs="112"/><title>Collection of hymns, with musical notation</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i12"><locus from="110r" facs="112"> f. 110r, lower</locus><title>instruction for reciting asmat prayer</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i13"><locus from="111" to="112v" facs="113"/><title>Gǝ`ǝz poetic phrases and sentences</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i14"><locus from="112v" to="113r" facs="115"/><title>Collection of hymns, with musical notation</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i15"><locus from="113r" to="113v" facs="115"/><title>Gǝ`ǝz Qene poem</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i16"><locus from="114r" to="114v" facs="116"/><title>List of phrases from the book of Psalms, sung before the gospel readings, the <foreign xml:lang="gez">ምስባክ</foreign></title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i17"><locus from="115r" to="115v" facs="117"/><title>Historical note about Saint Yared</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">ወበውእቱ: መዋዕል: ሀሎ: ያሬድ: ቀሲስ: ዘአብርሃ: ለኢትዮጵያ: በማኅሌተ: ሃሌ: ሉያ: ዘተምሕረ: እምኀበ መላእክት: ዘነበረ: ቀዲእም: ምስለ: ቅዱሳን: በአኵስም: ዘእንበለ: ይትወሀቦ: ረድኤት: እንዘ: ይስእል:<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i18"><locus from="115v" facs="118"/><title>Continutation of phrases from the book of Psalms, sung before the gospel readings, the <foreign xml:lang="gez">ምስባክ</foreign></title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i19"><locus from="115v" facs="118"/><title>Excerpt from the Gospel</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i20"><locus from="115v" to="116r" facs="118"/><title>Spiritual fruit of reading the scriptures and prayer</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i21"><locus from="116r" facs="118"/><title>The reason why John wrote the book of Revelation</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i22"><locus from="116v" to="15v" facs="119"/><title>list of common names</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
